---
import { getLucideIcon } from '../lib/lucide';
---

<section id="impact" class="relative mb-20 pb-16 border-b border-zinc-200/50 dark:border-poi-border/40">
  <div class="space-y-5 text-zinc-600 dark:text-poi-muted">
    <p class="font-mono text-xs tracking-widest uppercase text-poi-blue">Impact</p>
    <p class="!mt-2 text-xl sm:text-2xl font-semibold leading-snug tracking-tight text-zinc-900 dark:text-poi-focus">
      マンション管理会社の外部CTOとして、現場のDXを推進。
    </p>
    <p class="text-sm leading-8">
      現場を長年担ってきたオーナーが経営側に移行したいという課題に対し、勤怠改善を起点に信頼関係を築き、法人化に向けた全面的な DX 支援を担当。
    </p>
  </div>

  <!-- 数値メトリクスカード -->
  <div class="mt-8 grid grid-cols-2 gap-3">
    <div class="rounded-xl border border-zinc-200 dark:border-poi-blue/20 bg-zinc-50 dark:bg-white/[0.03] p-5 transition-colors hover:border-zinc-300 dark:hover:border-poi-blue/40">
      <p class="font-mono text-2xl font-semibold text-zinc-900 dark:text-poi-blue tabular-nums">~5h</p>
      <p class="mt-1 text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-poi-muted leading-relaxed">月あたりの集計工数削減</p>
    </div>
    <div class="rounded-xl border border-zinc-200 dark:border-poi-blue/20 bg-zinc-50 dark:bg-white/[0.03] p-5 transition-colors hover:border-zinc-300 dark:hover:border-poi-blue/40">
      <p class="font-mono text-2xl font-semibold text-zinc-900 dark:text-poi-blue tabular-nums">3〜4万</p>
      <p class="mt-1 text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-poi-muted leading-relaxed">月あたりの申告差異抑制</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- 補足テキスト -->
  <p class="mt-6 text-sm leading-8 text-zinc-600 dark:text-poi-muted">
    NFC 打刻 → スプレッドシート自動同期 → 給与計算自動化。「カードをタッチするだけ」の UX で IT 未経験の現場に定着。既存の Excel・スプレッドシート運用を無理に変えず、自動化を後付けする設計方針。
  </p>

  <!-- 勤怠DX フロー図解 -->
  <div class="mt-6 flex items-center gap-2">
    <div class="flex-1 rounded-xl border border-zinc-200 dark:border-poi-blue/20 bg-zinc-50 dark:bg-white/[0.03] p-4 text-center">
      <svg
        xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
        width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24"
        fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"
        stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"
        class="mx-auto text-poi-blue mb-2"
        aria-hidden="true"
        set:html={getLucideIcon("id-card")}
      />
      <p class="text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-poi-muted">NFC 打刻</p>
    </div>
    <svg
      xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
      width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24"
      fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"
      stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"
      class="shrink-0 text-zinc-400 dark:text-zinc-600"
      aria-hidden="true"
      set:html={getLucideIcon("arrow-right")}
    />
    <div class="flex-1 rounded-xl border border-zinc-200 dark:border-poi-blue/20 bg-zinc-50 dark:bg-white/[0.03] p-4 text-center">
      <svg
        xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
        width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24"
        fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"
        stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"
        class="mx-auto text-poi-blue mb-2"
        aria-hidden="true"
        set:html={getLucideIcon("table")}
      />
      <p class="text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-poi-muted">スプレッドシート同期</p>
    </div>
    <svg
      xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
      width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24"
      fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"
      stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"
      class="shrink-0 text-zinc-400 dark:text-zinc-600"
      aria-hidden="true"
      set:html={getLucideIcon("arrow-right")}
    />
    <div class="flex-1 rounded-xl border border-zinc-200 dark:border-poi-blue/20 bg-zinc-50 dark:bg-white/[0.03] p-4 text-center">
      <svg
        xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
        width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24"
        fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"
        stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"
        class="mx-auto text-poi-blue mb-2"
        aria-hidden="true"
        set:html={getLucideIcon("calculator")}
      />
      <p class="text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-poi-muted">給与計算自動化</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
